    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2007-05-17</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2007-06-12T20:05:29Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Teacher Education for Autistic Children Act of 2007 or the TEACH Act of 2007 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow a refundable income tax credit for up to $10,000 of the annual education expenses (e.g., tuition, books, student loan interest) incurred by individuals studying to become teachers of children or adults with an autism spectrum disorder. Terminates such credit after 2012. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
